jde.wizards

Class MethodFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • jde.wizards.MethodFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassRegistry
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DelegateFactory, InterfaceFactory, MethodOverrideFactory

    public class MethodFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassRegistry
    Defines a factory for creating skeleton implementations of Java interfaces. The factory can be invoked from the command line or from another program. The factory can generate implementations for multiple interfaces when invoked from the command line. Copyright (C) 1998-2004 Eric D. Friedman . All Rights Reserved. Copyright (C) 1998-2002 Paul Kinnucan .
